<section id="section-abstract">
      <h2 id="abstract"><a href="#abstract" class="selfRef">Abstract</a></h2>
<p id="section-abstract-1">Fastmail uses a number of keywords and mailbox names to implement mail functionality that others may wish to interoperate with. This document notes what they are and how to use them, and registers them with IANA to avoid name collisions.<a href="#section-abstract-1" class="pilcrow">¶</a></p>
</section>
