</dd>
          <dd class="break"></dd>
<dt id="section-2.7-1.3">Purpose:</dt>
          <dd id="section-2.7-1.4"> Indicate to the client that a message was sent automatically as a response due to a user rule or setting.<a href="#section-2.7-1.4" class="pilcrow">¶</a>
</dd>
          <dd class="break"></dd>
<dt id="section-2.7-1.5">Private or Shared on a server:</dt>
